<template>
  <ContactPage />
</template>
<script>
import ContactPage from "~/components/pages/ContactPage";
export default {
  components: {
    ContactPage,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      breadcrumbs: [
        {
          url: process.env.APP_URL,
          text: this.$t("homepage"),
        },
        {
          url: process.env.APP_URL + this.$route.path,
          text: this.$t("atoms.links.contact"),
        },
      ],
    };
  },
  head() {
    return {
      title: this.$t("pages.contact.title"),
      titleTemplate: "%s – " + this.$t("atoms.name"),
    };
  },
  jsonld() {
    const items = this.breadcrumbs.map((item, index) => ({
      "@type": "ListItem",
      position: index + 1,
      item: {
        "@id": item.url,
        name: item.text,
      },
    }));
    return {
      "@context": "http://schema.org",
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      itemListElement: items,
    };
  },
};
</script>
